      "subtopicTitle": {
        "english": "Numerical Expressions",
        "hindi": "संख्यात्मक व्यंजक"
      },
      "knowPrompt": {
        "english": "Do you know this topic: Numerical Expressions?",
        "hindi": "क्या आप यह विषय जानते हैं: संख्यात्मक व्यंजक?"
      },
      "explanationTitle": {
        "english": "Numerical Expressions",
        "hindi": "संख्यात्मक व्यंजक"
      },
      "explanationParagraphs": [
        {
          "english": "A **numerical expression** is a combination of numbers and operations (+, -, ×, ÷). To simplify means to evaluate and find the single value.",
          "hindi": "**संख्यात्मक व्यंजक** संख्याओं और क्रियाओं (+, -, ×, ÷) का संयोजन है।"
        },
        {
          "english": "**BODMAS / Order of Operations:**\nWe must follow this order:\n1. **B** — Brackets (solve what's inside brackets first)\n2. **O** — Of (powers or \"of\")\n3. **D** — Division\n4. **M** — Multiplication\n5. **A** — Addition\n6. **S** — Subtraction",
          "hindi": "**BODMAS नियम (संक्रिया का क्रम):**\n1. **B** — कोष्ठक (Brackets)\n2. **O** — का (Of)\n3. **D** — भाग (Division)\n4. **M** — गुणा (Multiplication)\n5. **A** — जोड़ (Addition)\n6. **S** — घटाव (Subtraction)"
        },
        {
          "english": "**Key Rule:** Multiplication and Division BEFORE Addition and Subtraction.",
          "hindi": "**मुख्य नियम:** जोड़-घटाव से पहले गुणा-भाग करें।"
        },
        {
          "english": "**Example:** 15 + 6 × 4\n- First: 6 × 4 = 24 (Multiplication first!)\n- Then: 15 + 24 = **39**\n- (Do NOT do 15+6=21 first — that gives the wrong answer 84!)",
          "hindi": "**उदाहरण:** 15 + 6 × 4\n- पहले: 6 × 4 = 24\n- फिर: 15 + 24 = **39**"
        }
      ],
      "examples": [
        {
          "english": "**Example:** 15 + 6 × 4\n- First: 6 × 4 = 24 (Multiplication first!)\n- Then: 15 + 24 = **39**\n- (Do NOT do 15+6=21 first — that gives the wrong answer 84!)",
          "hindi": "**उदाहरण:** 15 + 6 × 4\n- पहले: 6 × 4 = 24\n- फिर: 15 + 24 = **39**"
        }
      ],
      "visuals": [],
