            "hindi": "सरल कीजिए: 15 + 6 × 4।"
          },
          "type": "TEXT_INPUT",
          "options": [],
          "correctOptionIndex": null,
          "acceptedAnswers": [
            "39"
          ],
          "hint": null,
          "wrongReason": {
            "english": "Step 1: Apply BODMAS — Multiplication before Addition.\n- 6 × 4 = 24\n\nStep 2: Now add.\n- 15 + 24 = **39**\n\n**Answer: 39**",
            "hindi": "चरण 1: BODMAS — पहले गुणा।\n- 6 × 4 = 24\n\nचरण 2: फिर जोड़।\n- 15 + 24 = **39**\n\n**उत्तर: 39**"
          },
          "supportExample": {
